room_title: Escape room " The Legend of Sasquatch" by Mission Escape Rooms in Annapolis
review: We had a great time.  We were celebrating family Christmas time together and did the Hansel and Gretel escape room. It was challenging but we made it out with 5 minutes to spare. We are already looking.forward to doing.it again.

room_title: Escape room " The Legend of Sasquatch" by Mission Escape Rooms in Annapolis
review: The Hansel and Gretel room was great, but the picture lighting is best! 10/10 would recommend!

room_title: Escape room " The Legend of Sasquatch" by Mission Escape Rooms in Annapolis
review: My friends and I tried Hansel and Gretel, it was so much fun and the room was decorated very nicely! We were in the dark so it was a bit difficult to see but we had flashlights that helped us find our clues. The staff were very friendly and patience with us. Definitely recommend!!!
